TEXT.S: = Kaliyawan = Gaga mniq Hwareyseyn Sincungsyang ka alang Kaliyawan. 1,751 sapah ka kneegu na sapah, 4,493 hiyi ka kana knhbragan na hiyi. Tnpusu seejiq o mangal 28% niqan 1,266 hiyi sp, rahuq na uxay tnpusu seejiq o mangal 72% niqan 3,227 hiyi koia. Kana ka kleegan seejiq ga, Amis 15%, Bunun 2%, Tayal 2%, Truku 6%, Kebalan 2%, Paiwan 1%, ni rahuq na o 1%.
